In this part, you perform two administrative tasks &ndash; create the origanization and add a user account.

An organization enables you to group related projects and provide scope for authorization rules. User accounts enable end users to access Chef Delivery through its web interface or from the command line.

Here's what you'll do:

1. [Connect to the Windows workstation](#step1)
1. [Log in to the Delivery web interface](#step2)
1. [Create the organization](#step3)
1. [Add a user](#step4)

