## 4. Add a user

Now you'll add a user.

Select **Users** from the drop-down menu in the upper right corner.

![](delivery/web_ui_admin_users.png)

Click **+**, then fill in the fields. If you're setting up the account for someone else, enter an initial password and then give that person the username and password.

Leave the **Enter SSH Public Key** field blank &ndash; the user will set that up in the next part. 

In practice, you would determine the appropriate [roles and permissions](https://docs.chef.io/release/delivery/delivery_users_and_roles.html#roles-and-permissions) for your user. For now, select all roles except for **admin**.

![](delivery/add_a_user.png)

When you're done, click **Save & Close**.

